controller

Class ExtractionController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.ExtractionController

  • public class ExtractionController
extends java.lang.Object
    The ExtractionController is the main controlling class of the application; It controls the main application thread and the extraction process and the Extractor. Furthermore it manages the interaction between ProfileController, ModuleController and StorageController, and it updates the user interfaces GUI and CLI. A FileMonitorDaemon is used to observe file changes of the files added to the application.
